msItem.title: Āghāz-i kitāb-i Vīsparad bā maʻnī-i Fārsī tarjumah kardah mīnavīsam

supportDesc.extent: 1 + 74 leaves + 6 : 315 x 277 (215 x 185) mm, bound to 320 x 279 mm

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in Avestan, Pahlavi, and Persian (nastaʻlīq).

binding.p: Bound in reddish brown leather over pulpboard; plain brown pastedowns.

origin.p: Copy completed in 1224 AY (Anno Yazdegirdi) by Mūbid Jamshīd Pashūtan Hurmazdʹyār Jāmāsp Sanjānah (f. 74v).

history.provenance: Gift of Jivanji Jamshedji Modi, December 4, 1911.
Formerly owned by Manookjee Sorabjee Ashburner (numerous stamps).
